    "context": "Text = \"Gross, but alright.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "abe5b651eacdd56e486127ea463b51d736adb9d564eea265f96e792ba6d5cabd",
    "original": "I'll pay the 200 crowns for that...some kind of gland?",
